<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>日子一天天过去了，艾伦渐渐长大了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她会在口袋里放些石头，这样她就不会飘起来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的父母也越来越喜欢这个 “轻轻公主”。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为有艾伦，王宫里总是充满了笑声，生活总是充满了快乐！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦17岁的时候，她的父母又开始担心起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然艾伦的笑声让每个人都很开心，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但她对所有的一切都是笑嘻嘻的，哪怕是不好的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>比如，每当王后哭泣的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦就会咯咯笑着说：“嘻嘻！妈妈，你的脸又出水了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68809</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每当国王发火的时候，艾伦就会像蝴蝶一样在他身边飞来飞去，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大笑着说：“爸爸，再做一次生气的表情！你看起来真傻！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，尴尬的事情发生了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95013</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦正和两个仆人一起散步，她们紧紧地抓着公主的手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，艾伦看到了国王，她抽出一只手挥了挥：“爸爸！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦想找一些石头放在口袋里，但她看到了一只又大又黑的癞蛤蟆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她抓住它，然后向国王跑去。她伸开双臂，想要亲吻他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，一阵风吹过，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>把公主吹向了旁边的侍卫——她飞进了年轻侍卫的怀里！啵！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公主亲在了侍卫的脸上，然后她举起癞蛤蟆，在另一边脸上打了一下！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公主咯咯笑了起来：“希望你喜欢这只癞蛤蟆！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公主一直不停地笑，国王的脸红了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151011</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这太尴尬了！”他想，“必须得做点儿什么了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，国王和王后派人叫来公主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172001</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦的口袋里只有几颗小石头，所以她花了很长时间才坐下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179527</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王清了清嗓子：“艾伦，你知道你和其他人是不一样的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，没有什么不一样！”艾伦笑了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是一个鼻子、两只眼睛和一张嘴，和其他人一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“认真点儿！”王后说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我就喜欢傻傻的！”艾伦又不停地笑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 国王看着王后：“现在怎么办？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208927</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只有一个办法了。”王后说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“必须请柯普和哈姆来了——我们王国最聪明的两位哲学家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>